titleDescription:
Established in 2002, THE ABSOLUTE GROUP is Thailand’s leading health and lifestyle company offering a comprehensive 360 Fitness  and wellness solution to its clients under various business entities and brands including:
1. Absolute You Studio (the largest Boutique Fitness Studios in Thailand and Singapore); 
2. Absolute Sanctuary in Koh Samui (Asia’s leading Wellness Fitness Resort);
3. Absolute FitFood (Revolutionary Heath Food Concept);
4. Absolute Anytime (Exercise Online platform); 
5.  Absolute U Management Asia (Wellness Fitness Hospitality Management).

The company’s vision is to grow to be the leader in Asia for Wellness and Fitness offerings.

